{"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setTargetCoordinate:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@CLLocationCoordinate2D","text":"CLLocationCoordinate2D","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"targetCoordinate","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"animated:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL","text":"BOOL","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"animated","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"targetCoordinate","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The target coordinate to fit within the viewport.","type":"text"}]}]},{"name":"animated","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If ","type":"text"},{"code":"YES","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", the map animates to fit the target within the map","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"view. If ","type":"text"},{"code":"NO","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", the map fits the target instantaneously.","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"By default, the target coordinate is set to an invalid coordinate, indicating"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"that there is no target. In course tracking mode, the target forms one of two"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"foci in the viewport, the other being the user location annotation. Typically,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the target is set to a destination or waypoint in a real-time navigation scene."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"As the user annotation moves toward the target, the map automatically zooms in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to fit both foci optimally within the viewport."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This method has no effect if the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"userTrackingMode"},{"type":"text","text":" property is set to a value"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"other than "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserTrackingMode\/MLNUserTrackingModeFollowWithCourse","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To specify a completion handler to execute after the animation finishes, use"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"-setTargetCoordinate:animated:completionHandler:"},{"type":"text","text":" method."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/setTargetCoordinate:animated:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"metadata":{"role":"symbol","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(im)setTargetCoordinate:animated:","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setTargetCoordinate:animated:"}],"title":"setTargetCoordinate:animated:","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setTargetCoordinate:animated:"}],"remoteSource":{"fileName":"MLNMapView.h","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapView.h#L775"},"roleHeading":"Instance Method","platforms":[],"symbolKind":"method"},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Deprecated. Sets the geographic coordinate that is the subject of observation as"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the user location is being tracked, with an optional transition animation."}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/settargetcoordinate:animated:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"]]},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView":{"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","kind":"symbol","title":"MLNMapView","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An interactive, customizable map view with an interface similar to the one"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"provided by Apple’s MapKit."}],"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMapView"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView/setTargetCoordinate:animated:":{"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setTargetCoordinate:animated:","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"setTargetCoordinate:animated:","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/settargetcoordinate:animated:","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Deprecated. Sets the geographic coordinate that is the subject of observation as"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the user location is being tracked, with an optional transition animation."}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/setTargetCoordinate:animated:","type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"kind":"symbol","title":"MapLibre","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","type":"topic","role":"collection"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNUserTrackingMode/MLNUserTrackingModeFollowWithCourse":{"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNUserTrackingModeFollowWithCourse","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"MLNUserTrackingModeFollowWithCourse","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnusertrackingmode\/mlnusertrackingmodefollowwithcourse","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The map follows the user location and rotates when the course changes."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Course represents the direction in which the device is traveling."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The default user location annotation shows a puck-shaped indicator"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"that rotates as the course changes."}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserTrackingMode\/MLNUserTrackingModeFollowWithCourse","type":"topic"}}}